WEBVTT

00:12.126 --> 00:13.250
[static drones]

00:13.250 --> 00:16.500
[bright tone]

00:16.500 --> 00:19.500
[tense jazzy music]

00:19.500 --> 00:26.542
♪ ♪

01:48.083 --> 01:50.792
- Oz,
the name on the street

01:50.792 --> 01:54.126
for the Oswald Maximum
Security Penitentiary.

01:54.126 --> 01:55.417
- [grunts]

01:55.417 --> 01:58.458
- Oz,
where after months of tension,

01:58.458 --> 02:00.126
a riot erupted.

02:00.126 --> 02:03.709
[alarm blaring]
[indistinct shouting]

02:03.709 --> 02:05.042
- Aah!

02:07.001 --> 02:08.542
- You can't get me now,
motherfucker.

02:08.542 --> 02:12.084
[indistinct shouting continues]
[alarm continues blaring]

02:12.084 --> 02:13.875
- The unit known as
"Emerald City"

02:13.875 --> 02:16.083
was overtaken
by its prisoners.

02:16.083 --> 02:19.834
The governor ordered
his troops to recapture it...

02:19.834 --> 02:22.333
by any means necessary.

02:22.333 --> 02:23.333
[gunshot]

02:23.333 --> 02:26.375
[glass shatters, clattering]

02:33.792 --> 02:36.542
[gunshots]

02:36.542 --> 02:38.834
When the smoke cleared--
literally,

02:38.834 --> 02:42.166
six prisoners
and two correctional officers

02:42.166 --> 02:44.042
were dead,

02:44.042 --> 02:46.001
34 others were injured.

02:46.917 --> 02:48.333
- [coughing]

02:48.333 --> 02:50.750
- Some overcome by the gas...

02:50.750 --> 02:52.917
- [coughing]

02:52.917 --> 02:55.167
- Some from the beatings...

02:55.167 --> 02:58.209
[indistinct yelling]

02:59.166 --> 03:01.167
Some from rifle wounds.

03:01.167 --> 03:04.042
[gunshots]

03:04.042 --> 03:07.875
Among those shot,
Tim McManus,

03:07.875 --> 03:10.125
who invented Emerald City,

03:10.125 --> 03:12.000
and some say

03:12.000 --> 03:15.625
ran it into the ground.

03:15.625 --> 03:17.167
[indistinct frantic voices]

03:17.167 --> 03:21.042
[bell ringing]
[indistinct shouting]

03:21.042 --> 03:24.083
The rest of the prisoners
were moved

03:24.083 --> 03:25.417
