- Governor Devlin--

04:42.125 --> 04:44.001
- Fuck you, Governor.

04:44.001 --> 04:45.792
- What?
Am I asking so much?

04:45.792 --> 04:48.209
- You want me to come out
on your side.

04:48.209 --> 04:51.001
You want to close down
Emerald City permanently.

04:51.001 --> 04:52.375
You want me to say
that the prisoners

04:52.375 --> 04:55.208
are guilty of everything,
and you were totally justified

04:55.208 --> 04:57.209
