of those eight dead.

05:01.000 --> 05:04.001
- My hands are clean.
My conscience is clear.

05:04.001 --> 05:05.208
- Well, then back off

05:05.208 --> 05:06.834
and let me do
what you appointed me to do.

05:07.709 --> 05:10.291
- Okay.

05:10.291 --> 05:13.126
