other thing in mind,

05:13.126 --> 05:15.083
Mervin Suttel
is stepping down

05:15.083 --> 05:17.208
as state's attorney general.

05:17.208 --> 05:20.542
I'm looking for just
the right man to replace him.

05:22.126 --> 05:26.041
Come in, Warden,
we're done.

05:26.041 --> 05:28.709
Find the truth, Case,

05:28.709 --> 05:32.000
