shall set your fee.

05:33.208 --> 05:35.209
[door slams]
- [chuckling]

05:35.209 --> 05:36.917
"The truth."

05:36.917 --> 05:39.166
What is the truth, Leo?

05:39.166 --> 05:41.667
Is Devlin guilty?

05:41.667 --> 05:43.709
Are you?

05:45.209 --> 05:47.792
Leo...

05:47.792 --> 05:51.209
