and get a good night's nap.

09:15.166 --> 09:17.083
Yeah, right.

09:17.083 --> 09:20.709
- [panting]

09:20.709 --> 09:22.583
- Mr. McManus?

09:24.625 --> 09:26.166
Mr. McManus?

09:26.166 --> 09:27.709
Alvah Case.

09:30.042 --> 09:32.875
- Oh, yes.
