to dismantle Em City

09:41.209 --> 09:43.291
since the beginning.

09:43.291 --> 09:45.125
This is his chance.

09:45.125 --> 09:48.500
- Ooh, Leo told me
you'd be tough.

09:48.500 --> 09:51.041
He says you two
aren't always in agreement,

09:51.041 --> 09:54.625
