your ideals.

09:54.625 --> 09:58.750
- What is it
you want exactly?

09:58.750 --> 09:59.959
- I want to ask some questions.

10:00.750 --> 10:03.792
♪ ♪

10:03.792 --> 10:06.208
- I have nothing to say.

10:06.208 --> 10:08.333
