some preliminary interviews.

10:13.375 --> 10:16.001
- I have nothing to say.

10:16.001 --> 10:18.041
- Look...

10:18.041 --> 10:20.458
ultimately it's going
to be up to me

10:20.458 --> 10:24.001
to decide if Em City
ever reopens.

10:24.001 --> 10:30.333
♪ ♪

10:30.333 --> 10:32.375
- I have nothing to say.

10:33.959 --> 10:37.042
[door clanging open]

10:38.542 --> 10:40.000
- Minister Said?

10:42.166 --> 10:43.542
- As-salaam alaykum.

10:46.000 --> 10:48.500
- Alvah Case.

10:48.500 --> 10:51.083
I'm here to interview you
about the riot.

10:51.083 --> 10:54.709
- Is that interview
or interrogate?

10:54.709 --> 10:57.750
- I guess that depends on
what you're guilty of.

10:57.750 --> 10:59.375
- There was no riot.

10:59.375 --> 11:01.959
- Oh, really?

11:01.959 --> 11:03.291
- There was a righteous struggle

11:03.291 --> 11:05.333
against repression
and injustice.

11:05.333 --> 11:07.583
- Well, righteous or not,

11:07.583 --> 11:10.792
there are still eight bodies

11:10.792 --> 11:12.667
rotting in the morgue.

11:15.084 --> 11:16.875
- I grieve their deaths.

11:19.166 --> 11:21.750
- Do you mind?
- Please.

11:26.667 --> 11:28.875
- I understand that from
the minute you came to Oz

11:28.875 --> 11:31.208
you started organizing
other Muslims,

11:31.208 --> 11:34.126
converting stone-cold
killers,

11:34.126 --> 11:38.417
all the while sowing seeds
of discontent.

11:38.417 --> 11:42.125
- I spoke the truth.
- Then speak it now.

11:42.125 --> 11:44.250
Oh, come on, Said.

11:44.250 --> 11:47.041
