about the truth,

11:47.041 --> 11:49.917
but how come it doesn't include
taking responsibility

11:49.917 --> 11:52.167
for what you've done?
- I didn't fire those rifles.

11:52.167 --> 11:54.042
- Did you create
a set of circumstances

11:54.042 --> 11:55.667
that caused the rifles
to be fired?

11:55.667 --> 11:59.208
- The judicial system created
those circumstances, not I.

11:59.208 --> 12:02.041
Your commission is a fraud,
Case.

12:02.041 --> 12:04.417
Governor Devlin--
the one man whose actions

12:04.417 --> 12:09.000
should be investigated,
is the man that appointed you.

12:09.000 --> 12:12.042
That's like me getting to
pick the injury at my own trial.

12:15.834 --> 12:18.875
- [breathing heavily,
singing in foreign language]

12:24.041 --> 12:26.291
You want to lick my balls?

12:28.375 --> 12:31.417
[continues singing
in foreign language]

12:38.084 --> 12:41.041
[overlapping shouting]

12:41.041 --> 12:45.000
