will focus on events

12:45.000 --> 12:46.834
leading up to the riot.

12:46.834 --> 12:50.458
Bishop Callahan and Mr. Dodge
will deal with the behavior

12:50.458 --> 12:53.291
of the inmates and the staff
during the riot.

12:53.291 --> 12:56.625
