as long as it takes.

13:05.959 --> 13:07.917
[overlapping questions]

13:12.750 --> 13:16.333
- And you're...
- Augustus Hill.

13:16.333 --> 13:19.042
- Hill. Hill. Hill.
Hill. Hill.

13:19.042 --> 13:20.959
- Hey, can I ask you
a question?

13:20.959 --> 13:22.917
Two prisoners got
released on the riot.

13:22.917 --> 13:25.291
Eugene Dobbins,
Jackson Vahue.

13:25.291 --> 13:27.042
- Shut the fuck up.
