led to the riot.

13:42.834 --> 13:44.166
[overlapping shouting,
commotion]

13:44.166 --> 13:47.042
- These men are violent.
All they know is violence.

13:47.042 --> 13:50.083
- The COs, man,
they treat us like shit.

13:50.083 --> 13:52.917
- Sometimes the inmates
get bored.

13:52.917 --> 13:54.667
- They took away conjugals.

13:54.667 --> 13:56.208
